Interface Processor<RESULT extends Result,BATCH_RESULT extends BatchResult<RESULT>>

  • Type Parameters:
    RESULT - Type of validation result.
    BATCH_RESULT - Type of batch validation result.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvwProcessor

    public interface Processor<RESULT extends Result,BATCH_RESULT extends BatchResult<RESULT>>
    Main logic of validator, which performs all steps from which validation composed.
